00:13:04.820 --> 00:13:05.540
Right.

00:13:05.600 --> 00:13:13.240
And that that becomes fun and that becomes amazing, even if it wasn't necessarily like what you did in your spare time originally or something.

00:13:13.240 --> 00:13:13.240
Right.

00:13:13.240 --> 00:13:13.520
Right.

00:13:13.520 --> 00:13:15.860
So I think there's there's a lot to motivate people there.

00:13:15.860 --> 00:13:16.400
Absolutely.

