And it's like, oh, no, I probably shouldn't have done this to myself.

00:14:06.380 --> 00:14:17.380
So taking the time to look and examine what is actually happening and what will be required of you, in this case, kind of like how you would use get fetch instead of get pull.

00:14:17.380 --> 00:14:20.960
That way you can see the changes that have been made so you don't make bigger mistakes.

00:14:20.960 --> 00:14:22.720
